OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussia's Putin condemns    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'mad and thoughtless'      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FWestern sanctions          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The sanctions imposed by the West on   
OL,6, Russia after its invasion of Ukraine   
OL,7, are "mad and thoughtless", President   
OL,8, Vladimir Putin has said.               
OL,10,FSpeaking at a forum in St Petersburg,  
OL,11,Fhe said "the economic blitzkrieg       
OL,12,Fagainst Russia had no chance of        
OL,13,Fsucceeding from the very beginning".   
OL,15,FHe said the restrictions were "more    
OL,16,Fharmful" to those who imposed them.    
OL,18,FWestern nations have been seeking to   
OL,19,Fstrike a balance between punishing     
OL,20,FRussia and protecting their economies. 
